uk.ac.ed.inf.powergrab

Class Position

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.inf.powergrab.Position
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Geography

    public class Position
extends java.lang.Object
implements Geography
    The Position class used to indicate a geographic position, and provides position related methods.

    A object of Position class is a basic geographic element, which implemented Geography interface. Also provides function to calculate the next position in a specific direction, and to judge whether this position is in play area.
